Download data: Interactive Map




An interactive map is available that facilitates the selection and download of information.


When clicking on one grid in the map, a panel is displayed showing the content of its attributes. The item '
Documentos:
' allows you to download the existing files for the selected element.






#map {
       width: 100%;
       height: 50vh;
       border: 1px solid cornflowerblue;
     }








    var iderioja_config = {
    "consulta": "46757a356c32636e39766143325861395a2b352b4c773d3d",
    "fondo_base": 1,
    "popup": 2
    };










On the IDErioja website, there is an 
index
 of all the interactive maps available from La Rioja Government.


Once a map is opened, by clicking on its title, it is possible to carry out a search on the fly in order to select any other map.

